  "detailed_description": "The MAKAI is in crisis...<br>Eldied and Diana, two demon girls, leave on a quest to defeat the main evil.<br><br>Get past the Danmaku and try to clear it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/fa919592efcbe174dcf1094d2d06fd7b.avif?t=1667009442\" width=616 height=148 /></span><br>Aggressive play is the closest you'll get to capturing it, and this is a Danmaku shooter with a Rank System.<br>Defeating enemy, Graze a bullet, Shooting enemy...<br>All of these active actions lead to Power Up.<br><br>You can use the power you've saved to maintain a strong shot and attack it,<br>You can also use a buster attack to eliminate enemy bullets while blowing them away,<br>Your play style depends on your ability.<br><br>The beauty of the Danmaku and the pleasure of the Shooter is Here!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/dbfc11b974f505097153e3b7d7ec3f97.poster.avif?t=1667009442\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/dbfc11b974f505097153e3b7d7ec3f97.webm?t=1667009442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/dbfc11b974f505097153e3b7d7ec3f97.mp4?t=1667009442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/9003ccd03ff6813c46da8753ff6c3a99.avif?t=1667009442\" width=616 height=148 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6+1 total 7 Stages.<br></li><li>2 Playable Character(and more).<br></li><li>４ levels of Difficulty for beginners and professionals.<br></li><li>11 MAKAI Girls.<br></li><li>Challenge Mode for the Danmaku maniacs! (Let's clear!)<br></li><li>Replay viewer.<br></li><li>Music room.<br></li><li>Pixel art graphics.<br></li><li>A little cat element.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/e07b780cf7d059a7baec4530becb542d.poster.avif?t=1667009442\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/e07b780cf7d059a7baec4530becb542d.webm?t=1667009442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/e07b780cf7d059a7baec4530becb542d.mp4?t=1667009442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The MAKAI is in crisis...<br>Eldied and Diana, two demon girls, leave on a quest to defeat the main evil.<br><br>Get past the Danmaku and try to clear it!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/fa919592efcbe174dcf1094d2d06fd7b.avif?t=1667009442\" width=616 height=148 /></span><br>Aggressive play is the closest you'll get to capturing it, and this is a Danmaku shooter with a Rank System.<br>Defeating enemy, Graze a bullet, Shooting enemy...<br>All of these active actions lead to Power Up.<br><br>You can use the power you've saved to maintain a strong shot and attack it,<br>You can also use a buster attack to eliminate enemy bullets while blowing them away,<br>Your play style depends on your ability.<br><br>The beauty of the Danmaku and the pleasure of the Shooter is Here!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/dbfc11b974f505097153e3b7d7ec3f97.poster.avif?t=1667009442\" width=616 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/dbfc11b974f505097153e3b7d7ec3f97.webm?t=1667009442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/dbfc11b974f505097153e3b7d7ec3f97.mp4?t=1667009442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388230/extras/9003ccd03ff6813c46da8753ff6c3a99.avif?t=1667009442\" width=616 height=148 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6+1 total 7 Stages.<br></li><li>2 Playable Character(and more).<br></li><li>４ levels of Difficulty for beginners and professionals.<br></li><li>11 MAKAI Girls.<br></li><li>Challenge Mode for the Danmaku maniacs! (L